# =============================================================================
# AUTHENTICATION SERVICE - ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# =============================================================================
# Lý thuyết: Environment Configuration
# - Tách config khỏi code (12-factor app)
# - Dễ thay đổi giữa environments (dev, staging, prod)
